article.headline: Northern Arizona 78, UC Davis 50
article.story: FLAGSTAFF, Ariz. (AP) -- Kyle Landry scored 15 points in 20 minutes to lead Northern Arizona to a 78-50 victory over UC Davis on Saturday. None of the starters played more than 32 minutes as the Lumberjacks took a 38-25 halftime lead and never lost control of the game. Landry was 4-of-5 from the floor and 7-of-7 on free throws. Kelly Golob had 13 points for the Lumberjacks (2-2), and Ruben Boykin Jr. had eight points and eight rebounds. Phil Rasmussen had 14 points and Thomas Juillerat 12 for the Aggies (1-2).
